                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                  <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                  <button type="button" class="btn btn-danger" id="movspin">SPIN!</button>
                </div>
                </form>
              </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>


        <hr class="my-4">
          <p class="text-light text-center">We have numerous payment options available through PayPal. We will provide a payment link in your return email after your reservation is finalized. We can also accept traditional forms of payment such as check, cash, or money order.</p>
